[![](https://i2.wp.com/www.onemanandhisblog.com/content/images/2004/10/875770_043f45266f.jpg?w=960)](http://www.flickr.com/photos/adders/875770/ "photo sharing") [Leaf & Logo](http://www.flickr.com/photos/adders/875770/), originally uploaded by [Adam Tinworth](http://www.flickr.com/people/adders/).
Entered for [Photo Friday](http://www.photofriday.com/) : [2 by 4](http://www.photofriday.com/archives/challenge/000374.php). I walked my two blocks north and four blocks east from work and found myself in a little alley tucked away off Theobold’s Road. This was the most satisfying of the images I took, catching the moment when Autumn and a lawyer’s car became one.
